int Der Grozzer.... Most all Succesful men/women are in the position they are in because they know how to cover their weakness' . ie Get the right people for the right jobs. So even tho you are attempting to give Bush's popularity to his speech writers I am forced to inform you of the obvious. Bush knows he is weak in the public speaking forum but he is smart enough to have on hand the ones that can cover that weakness. Maybe you should hire someone to post on the boards for you. <p>Krickett Buffslinger<BR> Shamaness of the Tribunal<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uelcheproudfoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elche Proudfoot</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mmmmm lobster</span><br>  Posts: 464<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(1/31/02 6:24:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://images.about.com/specials/service/promotion/sod/male_lead_stealer/josh_ryan_evans.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> most politicians have speechwriters create their words. not really a crime<br><br><br>Bush's speach reminded me of a 7th graders first 5 paragraph essay, with a tripartite topic sentence in the first paragraph. <br><br> <p><font size="-2" face="verdana">Elche Proudfoot<BR><b>Founder and Chief Mystic</font><br><font color=red size="-2" face="verdana"> Shining Path</FONT></b> </FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A