><br>The branches of service go from USMC, USA, USN, and USAF from hardest boot camp to easiest.  Had I started all over again I probably would have done USAF over Navy, but it's still been an easy 5 years with less actual &quot;work&quot; than any civillian job I had prior.<br><br>Of course, don't even think about it if you can't handle getting yelled at for no reason, can't follow simple instructions, or get teary being away from friends and family for extended periods. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/umertondraco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Merton Draco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Devout Worshipper of<br>Rangers and Paladins...</span><br>  Posts: 973<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(1/31/02 8:52:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EZ road to better life</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>Could you please... explain what Homeland Security is?<br><br>Don't know? Neither does Bush.<br><hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>Oh he definitely knows.  But if he divulged the true nature of &quot;Homeland Security&quot;, Americans would be rioting.<br><br>Homeland Security is a cutesy non-hostile term that basically signals the beginning of a government agency which will operate very similarly to the Nazi Gestapo in the next few decades.  And if you think that the Constitution will protect you, you will be mistaken.<br><br>Arleanna said half-jokingly (at least I am assuming half-jokingly) that the Bush's will become a dynasty with Jeb taking over after George's 2 terms.  I am afraid that may not be too far out of the realm of possibility.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% va